:

1. *Smrti* je neizbežan deo života. (Death is an inevitable part of life.)
2. *Smrti* su nevolje u koje se ne može verovati. (Deaths are misfortunes one cannot believe.)
3. On je postao uzoran čovek iako je bio blizu *smrti*. (He became an exemplary man even though he was close to death.)
4. *Smrti* su imale teške posledice na porodicu. (Deaths had severe consequences on the family.)